Brazilian prosecutors said Wednesday they were  investigating reports that football star Neymar has organized a New Year's Eve mega-party at his luxury home near Rio de Janeiro, despite public health measures to curb rising coronavirus deaths.
Sources close to the striker denied he had plans to host such an extravaganza, while the Paris Saint-Germain player added to the mystery by simply posting pictures of himself with a friend on a yacht off a beach in the southern state of Santa Catarina. 



